definition: a rectangular area surrounded on all sides by buildings
details:
noun
- a rectangular area surrounded on all sides by buildings
= synonyms: quadrangle
- (printing) a block of type without a raised letter
= synonyms: space
- a muscle of the thigh that extends the leg
= synonyms: musculus quadriceps femoris, quadriceps
- one of four children born at the same time from the same pregnancy
= synonyms: quadruplet
